#install light and configure light for brightness functionality on i3 or openbox in arch linux

1. sudo pacman -S light
2. sudo chmod +x /usr/bin/light (optional)
3. sudo usermod -a -G video $LOGNAME (add current user to video grup)
4. type 'groups' in terminal (if the video group does'nt appear log out and log in to apply these changes)
5. use these command for brightness functionality:
	- exec light -A 20 (increase brightness)
	- exec light -U 20 (decrease brightness)
6. refresh your current window manager
7. done